  ('Cookie Pie', 20, 'dessert', '{"Dessert"}'::text[], 'A giant, fudgy almond butter cookie baked in a pie dish — crisp on the edges, soft and gooey in the center. Naturally sweetened with honey, grain-free, and incredibly easy to make.'),
